net.sf.jmuserver.gs.muObjects
Class MuItemStats

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.jmuserver.gs.muObjects.MuItemStats

public class MuItemStats
extends java.lang.Object

Contains all item types and stats, which are loaded ONCE from file when initiating the world environment. Any item in game must have a reference to an instance of this class.

Author:
Marcel
See Also:
MuInventoryItem, MuItemOnGround
